ABOUT
This plugin is used to check if there are CJK characters in comment against spam coz almost all the spam comments are in English.

HISTORY
  06/01.2009  0.1.0  First release

INSTALL
-----------------------------------
1. Drop somechinese folder into habari/user/plugins
2. Go to admin panel and active plugin
3. Optional: You can configure the notification text from admin panel
4. Optional: You can use code below to show the notification text in your template:
     <?php echo Options::get ('cjkplease_text'); ?>
